Name: Songs to Make Your Bread Rise
Description:
Take your time, keep warm.  Bread takes hours to rise, so something you could listen to for a while during the wait. Bonus points if the song envelopes you like a warm blanket, since bread usually rises better at warm room temperatures.

Clarification. Prompt is not meant to be sexual.
